itemDisplayName: Deploy a 5 Node Service Fabric Cluster and an OMS workspace completely configured to monitor Service Fabric
description: This template allows you to deploy a 5 node Service fabric Cluster running Windows server 2012 R2 Data center, an OMS Workspace, and add the diagnostic storage account to the workspace and enable the Service Fabric Gallery solution
summary: This template takes a minimum amount of parameters and deploys 5  Node Service Fabric Cluster into OMS
